{"tid":1324211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[蠢閪有樣睇] 倡停批不反對通知書　蔣麗芸自爆民建聯無人欲聯名","createTime":"2019-07-16T13:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T05:03:32.000Z","uid":224066,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ba9cd4a168a97b5ff5860328b89625448649686c","tid":1324211,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"早前沙田大遊行（14日）後，沙田新城市廣場釀流血衝突。民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸昨日曾發表公開信，促請警務處暫停批出可能引起騷亂的集會遊行「不反對通知書」。<br />\n<br />\n蔣麗芸今日（16日）出席商台節目《在晴朗的一天出發》時，被問及有關意見是否代表民建聯發表，她回應僅屬個人意見，並非民建聯立場。<br />\n<br />\n她更「自爆」發出公開信前，曾用兩日時間在民建聯群組提出有關建議，<span style=\"color: red;\">但最終並無黨友要求聯名</span>，亦未收到指令不能發表公開信，故最後決定以個人身份發表。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3037899/org/5121320ae0fc72bd1700ae23b9cd418b.JPG/RQodiEbUYEHb2eMCOKTAJ-V4C87XEjYEqSUxdqklMXY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3037899%2Forg%2F5121320ae0fc72bd1700ae23b9cd418b.JPG%2FRQodiEbUYEHb2eMCOKTAJ-V4C87XEjYEqSUxdqklMXY&h=e84f1373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>以嘆息回應上次「割席」事件 決定獲網民支持</strong><br />\n<br />\n出席同一節目的公民黨黨魁楊岳橋詢問蔣麗芸的公開信，是代表個人或是民建聯立場，蔣麗芸先回應：「哎啊！你這一條問題真是好喇！」及後她強調，其言論都是本人意見，與民建聯無關。<br />\n<br />\n對於蔣麗芸突然「自我割席」，電台主持人追問她，上次民建聯就她對《逃犯條例》的言論「割席」，是否對她造成陰影及傷害，她深嘆一聲<span style=\"color: red;\">：「唉&hellip;&hellip;老實講啦，有咩未見過啊？好多風雨我都可以承受&hellip;&hellip;我今日一日係議員，我一日都要本住良心講出事實真相！」</span><br />\n<br />\n她又指，在發出公開信前，曾用兩日時間在民建聯群組提出，惟未有收到黨友表示要聯名發信，亦未有人表明不能發出。因此，她昨日決定發表公開信。她說，自從在Facebook發佈相關帖文後，不少網民表示支持。"},{"pid":"509f1732b58f8b741b686f1033d09dc8c2b52c23","tid":1324211,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:25:56.000Z","msg":"會唔會凍結佢黨籍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a760c1dec28ee11d1f94bbf597ef6a5dd26b73f9","tid":1324211,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:30:14.000Z","msg":"好快無得做架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b3d92315f4bb491fb006d1fd0968af2bb85313","tid":1324211,"uid":61340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:35:24.000Z","msg":"呢條友想保住個位 就學其他人 咁收皮喇 <br />\n做議員做到咁唔識睇風向"},{"pid":"c74e25ff32d3af3c656f39f3e986f4beeee701de","tid":1324211,"uid":25656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"拎外國細力證據出黎先講啦"},{"pid":"138121c348af9ddc94e5c39e612f7c99db6fd9c2","tid":1324211,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"遊行集會權利係基本法寫明，佢要佢個黨陪佢帶頭反基本法？"},{"pid":"a2149e5ce64d328086b0d3856b82db7b8f879041","tid":1324211,"uid":118125,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:39:42.000Z","msg":"分分鐘民建聯圍內開多個group冇元秋呢位豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n停批不反對通知書，咪即係警方贊成遊行路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283c96b85c8f847496cf5fde404c4f4619366c7e","tid":1324211,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:41:08.000Z","msg":"蔣麗云姐姐<br />\n請你繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n市民需要你做對手"},{"pid":"9b50915c81a03289c5b47710f2d43a23a003eebd","tid":1324211,"uid":23705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:45:59.000Z","msg":"你呢友傻架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9558af03591ab1c48c4d701d2b4f452de90216","tid":1324211,"uid":267600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:56:04.000Z","msg":"笨蛋做笨事！"},{"pid":"44e0a05a08118fc5c8c907204165977b2ddcfb74","tid":1324211,"uid":277913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:01:23.000Z","msg":"你以為蔣元秋係共產黨員，其實佢係蔣系國民黨嘅特務，協助香港人反共救國，光復我大中華民國。"},{"pid":"142545e078d3cef2668dcc90783285cacee614cf","tid":1324211,"uid":256014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:55:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">　　蔣麗芸，</span>白閪痴<span style=\"color: brown;\">（所以，</span><span style=\"color: red;\">其他</span><span style=\"color: green;\">民建聯議員</span>無出聲），<span style=\"color: red;\">暫停批出</span>「不反對通知書」，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">　　如果</span><span style=\"color: red;\">暫停批出</span>「不反對通知書」<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">期間，</span><span style=\"color: green;\">林鄭月娥</span>條死八婆<span style=\"color: red;\">有做過嘢，</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">局面</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">就可以</span><span style=\"color: red;\">緩和，</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">但</span><span style=\"color: red;\">照舊做</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">SHOW</span>跟稿讀，不能夠降溫，<span style=\"color: red;\">再加上</span>不讓<span style=\"color: green;\">香港人</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">遊行，</span><span style=\"color: red;\">攘到</span>無自由，無人權，仲衰。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"2bf0c6bca3956655032db8643d1fce06baf06e15","tid":1324211,"uid":278298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"唔係見呢個豬閪有錢，一早踢撚咗佢出黨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58541c3e9d2f66e7b5cda64defd729ea5648cdc","tid":1324211,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:03:32.000Z","msg":"Ann姐好撚慘㗎，原本坐定粒六繼續選九西，點知政府屎忽痕DQ多兩個，搞到多咗個鄭泳舜同陳健康，下年塊餅都唔知有冇佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}